&lt;p&gt;Fair comments. I have corrected the inconsistencies that you have mentioned. The transaction chapter in the remains for the most part unchanged; I have also documented the spring-tx.xsd schema file with inline comments.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll wait for more feedback concerning the transaction chapter (I wrote all the new Spring 2.0 parts); the chpater that you are reading now is my first draft, plus changes from one person proofreading said chapter. if you have any more comments about the &apos;flow&apos; of the transaction documentation, please do post them on this issue (or mail me directly) and I will incorporate any criticisms you may have.&lt;/p&gt;

